Package menu

Class ManagerMenu

java.lang.Object
menu.ManagerMenu
public class ManagerMenu extends Object
This class represents the menu interface for Project Managers. It provides functionality for managers to create, edit, and delete projects, process applications and withdrawal requests, manage officer registrations, and generate various reports.
